
=============================
=      File description     =
=============================
Book.java - implements the book class to be stored in a library.
Patron.java - implements the patron class, who can borrow books and critique
them.
Library.java - implements a library, which stored books and patrons.
patrons can borrow and return books from the library, and the library can
suggest a book to a patron depending on his tast
ex0.pdf - Excersize instructions



=============================
=          Design           =
=============================
For this assignment, i decided to store the books and tha patrons in arrays
as part of the library object, for the sake of simplicity. the index number
of the cell in which the book or the patron is stored in the array is its id 
number.



